snippet.title: New Neo-Geo Game : Cyborg Force - Preorder Trailer
snippet.description:
Cyborg Force is a "run & gun" action game released primarily for the Neo Geo. It features 5 levels (divided into 2 sub-levels + 1 boss level), 2 player co-op, and aims to reproduce the 1990s arcade feel we love. Physical release on Neo Geo AES and MVS and rom-stick !

For more informations ,
https://www.neobyteforce.com

or just chat with the devs you can join their discord:
https://discord.gg/yV3HsEYGgp

Video Edit : Charles Mulder

#neogeo #neogeoaes #neogeomvs #retrogaming #retrogaminglife
